label: Hermetschwil, Benediktinerinnenkloster, Cod. chart. 139

metadata.label: Summary (English)
metadata.value: This book of hours belonged to Johannes Huber (†1500), chaplain at the Grossmünster in Zurich. It contains parts of prayers related to the Liturgy of the Hours for the daily routine of clerics.
